Besides,
he treated this patient for a long time.

4
00:00:50,759 --> 00:00:52,761
Gang-hwa must be having a hard time.

5
00:00:53,511 --> 00:00:55,722
Geun-sang couldn't even talk to him.

6
00:01:07,442 --> 00:01:09,736
YANGSEO 12

7
