What?

64
00:12:09,562 --> 00:12:11,605
Okay. I'm on my way now.

65
00:12:23,409 --> 00:12:24,243
Where are you going?

66
00:12:24,326 --> 00:12:26,537
I just got a call from the hospital.

67
00:12:26,620 --> 00:12:29,165
